<div
  class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row h-screen justify-center items-center mt-40 sm:mt-16"
>

  <div
    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-10 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-white w-full sm:w-4/5 md:w-3/5 bg-blue-500 bg-opacity-50 mx-auto"
  >
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4 text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold">REGISTRATE
      A MOTION SIM</h1>
    <p class="text-center mb-4 text-xl sm:text-2xl">
      Nuestra plataforma te ofrece una experiencia única de aprendizaje
      interactivo, donde podrás explorar simulaciones realistas de problemas de
      MRU y MRUV. Desde la comodidad de tu hogar, podrás experimentar y entender
      los conceptos clave de la cinemática de una manera emocionante y efectiva.
    </p>
    <a
      href="/index"
      class="mt-4 bg-white text-blue-500 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg"
    >Inicia Sesión</a>
  </div>
  <div
    class="block mx-2 sm:mx-auto my-2 sm:my-12 p-8 bg-white w-4/5 sm:w-4/5 md:w-1/3 border border-gray-200 rounded-lg shadow-lg text-gray-800"
  >
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">REGÍSTRATE</h1>
    <form action="" method="post" class="mt-4">

      <input
        type="text"
        name="name"
        placeholder="Name"
        class="border border-gray-200 w-full text-lg placeholder-gray-500 p-2 my-2 bg-gray-200 focus:bg-white"
        required
      />
      <input
        type="email"
        name="email"
        placeholder="Email"
        class="border border-gray-200 w-full text-lg placeholder-gray-500 p-2 my-2 bg-gray-200 focus:bg-white"
        required
      />
      <input
        type="password"
        name="password"
        placeholder="Password"
        class="border border-gray-200 w-full text-lg placeholder-gray-500 p-2 my-2 bg-gray-200 focus:bg-white"
        required
      />
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="rounded-md bg-green-500 w-full text-lg text-white font-semibold p-2 my-3 hover:bg-green-600 focus:bg-green-700"
      >Enviar</button>

      {{#if error}}
        <p class="text-red-500 font-bold text-lg my-3">{{error}}</p>
      {{/if}}
    </form>
  </div>
</div>